title: Cooking Pasta (2017) by Martha Stephenson (ePUB) [DeadLorde]
description:
If you have always wanted to make homemade pasta dishes from the comfort of your own home, then you have certainly come to the right place!

Inside this book, you will not only discover how to make pasta dishes from scratch; you will learn how to prepare various types of sauce, homemade pasta, and various pasta-inspired meals just the way most five-star Italian restaurants do. You will also discover 25 of the most delicious pasta recipes you will ever find
